originalText.text: Manager is a thief. Manager denied me monthly parking after his employee the night before assured me I could leave my car there overnight and set up monthly parking when the manager is working the next day. When I showed up the next morning the manager said they have no monthly spots available and I would have to pay the full amount for parking my car there overnight. I asked if I could get a discount on the overnight parking since I was misled and was told No without consideration. Avoid this garage!

originalText.text:
DO NOT LEAVE YOUR CAR AT THIS GARAGE
I made the mistake of leaving my car there and when I went to pick it up, I noticed scratches on my side door (I can tell because I can saw powder on the door as of it was scratched against a wall. I also saw two holes on the driver’s seat and surprisingly “candy”. As soon as I noticed this, I decided not to get inside the car and called the worker there to report this. The guy was not speaking English properly and called his manager. The manager started defending the garage by saying he can’t honor any of these damages and that he can’t find out how it’s done. Later, he claimed that he will view the camera recordings and give me a call the next day. I had no choice but to leave after he sent me a text message confirming that he’s going to view the cameras. He never called me and I when I contacted him, he kept delaying by saying “he’s busy” he will do it the next day. Once he reviewed the camera he contacted me to come the next day and said I can come at anytime and that he will be at the garage all day. I gave him a curtsy call to give him heads up before I arrive. He says he’s about to leave and to make it harder for me, he says he will be around on a weekend day. There was no proper customer service provided to me and he didn’t give me an option to contact another person so I can get to the bottom of this issue. I was almost at the garage so I stepped inside to ask if he had left and if there is anyone that can assist me. I was sent home with no help and was told that only one guy can help me and that the guy want not even at the garage as he was in a different location. I was misled, mistreated as a customer and this situation was not handled correctly. They lost a customer that would have used the garage service daily all to be sneaky and not do their due diligence to take care of my car and own up to their mistakes
